public class PresentationTopologyImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements PresentationTopology

An implementation of the model object ' Presentation Topology'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Presentation Nodes
  • Scene Transformation
  • Topology
  • Axis Visible
  • Scene Centroid
  • Drag And Drop Mode
